{"tid":791484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意寵物小精靈嘅你入一入","createTime":"2018-08-23T23:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T23:49:21.000Z","uid":40679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb53c09780b698f4ddf33c361d90683837bc306c","tid":791484,"uid":40679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:39:16.000Z","msg":"由細細個已經開始諗緊點樣令Pokemon更有真實感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPokemon Go一出嗰陣我都有玩過下 <br />\n但我覺得咁多人玩玩下放棄係因為冇嗰種真實擁有嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我喺到諗<br />\n如果將 Pokemon Go 嘅GPS同捉小精靈<br />\n加上 Nintendo版嘅戰鬥風格<br />\n再加上 真嘅精靈球 <br />\n整一個App<br />\n一定好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/073029_ae223586b9feef0e954bcf93d33d40f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F073029_ae223586b9feef0e954bcf93d33d40f7.png&h=d8729c04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/073034_af0d4cb2b56d9d88c1bc125a38437e10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F073034_af0d4cb2b56d9d88c1bc125a38437e10.png&h=4b3eef51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就好似圖中咁 但可以映射你隻小精靈出嚟<br />\n攞住你嘅精靈球，用好似QR code咁嘅野scan六隻出嚟同人對戰<br />\n輸咗就比虛擬幣比對方<br />\n虛擬幣就可以買藥比小精靈補血<br />\n大家都可以用真錢買空嘅精靈球 用App去捉小精靈<br />\n再入落精靈球到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣我就真係可以捉齊所有寵物小精靈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 9up，又要買版權，又要買投資，我做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7970fe21527395869307e867a9aec33b7f81a826","tid":791484,"uid":49055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:41:34.000Z","msg":"香港人 認真返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fab265f